  "description": "Are you struggling to get the Create Mod Interactive to work? We've got the perfect solution for you!",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3dc89ac43ceba618de804fafa7b24c0d2c869780.png\" alt=\"interactive+ title\">\n</p>\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <h3>Are you struggling to get the Create Mod Interactive to work? We've got the perfect solution for you!</h3>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <strong>Valkyrienskies Discord!</strong>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/tkjfGr7\">https://discord.com/invite/tkjfGr7</a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <ul>\n    <li>Please report only bugs related to the modpack, not the individual mods themselves. Your feedback helps us improve the overall experience!</li>\n  </ul>\n</p>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<details>\n<summary>Interactive Features</summary>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Train Derailment</h1>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <ul>\n    <li>The big one everyone has been asking for, Trains can finally derail off of tracks!</li>\n    <li>Trains also keep their momentum and can push other derailed trains while still on their tracks!</li>\n  </ul>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/XIApl0JMHu0\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Rotation Propagator Bearing</h1>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <ul>\n    <li>A modified mechanical bearing that propagates rotation to its contraption.</li>\n    <li>Especially useful for Sub-Contraptions!</li>\n  </ul>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/MyfCcqiE/images/01ae9b8cf7f45fe1eeb5456d0ed8a8065ebfed9e.gif\" alt=\"Rotation Propagator Bearing\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <ul>\n    <li>Also included is a disjointed variant, with propagated rotation controlled via an embedded cogwheel.</li>\n  </ul>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/MyfCcqiE/images/8f8026f881881d5841ab1dc3c26d6a6bd5f5450b.gif\" alt=\"Disjointed Rotation Propagator Bearing\">\n</p>\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Interactive Contraptions</h1>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <ul>\n    <li>Place and destroy blocks on contraptions just like regular Minecraft!</li>\n  </ul>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/IZBSAnO8qLw\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Train Buffer Stop</h1>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <ul>\n    <li>By default trains will roll off of tracks when they reach the end of the line!</li>\n    <li>Use Train Buffer Stops to prevent your train from rolling off the tracks</li>\n  </ul>\n</p>\n\n</details>\n</div>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/GjVxY_PsYks\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <blockquote>I am in no way affiliated with Mojang Studios, Microsoft or the valkyrienskies team and will never claim to be</blockquote>\n</p>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<details>\n<summary>Videos on the mod</summary>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/nTS8qVcpn-c\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Iyy7P_ZWFmk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/kFoYjnvdteo\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/MEExpzONaHI\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</p>\n\n</details>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<details>\n<summary>To Do</summary>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <ol>\n    <li>Add more mods that work with create interactive fabric</li>\n  </ol>\n</p>\n\n</details>\n</div>",
